dc_title_s: Law Enforcement Response Districts Jackson County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents law enforcement response districts in Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This digital geospatial dataset is a current representation of all Law Enforcement Zones in Jackson County, Wisconsin, with attributes standardized in accordance to the NENA Standard for NG9-1-1 GIS Data Model (NENA-STA-006.1-2018). Responding law enforcement agencies include the Black River Falls Police Department, Ho-Chunk Nation Police Department, Jackson County Sheriff's Office, Village of Melrose Police Department, and Village of Merrillan Police Department.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
